Title (EN): Community Enhancement Employment Program Annual Project List and Funding Provided

Description (EN): The Community Enhancement Employment Program (CEEP) is a provincially-funded program that provides short-term employment. Key clients include project sponsors and individuals in need of employment.
Description (FR): Le Community Enhancement Employment Program (CEEP) est un programme financé par la province qui fournit des emplois à court terme. Les principaux clients sont les promoteurs de projets et les personnes à la recherche d'un emploi.
